File: A general view of the headquarters of Eskom. AFP/Gianluigi Guercia JOHANNESBURG - Stage 2 power cuts will start at 10pm on Tuesday until 5am Wednesday. Load-shedding will take place at the same time on Wednesday night. Eskom blames unplanned maintenance for the outage. The utility also urges all South Africans to use electricity sparingly. #POWERALERT 1
